item.title: Ariel Winter on Bringing Sabrina Grimm to Life in 'The Sisters Grimm' on Apple TV+
item.description: Ariel Winter — you remember her as Alex Dunphy from Modern Family — joins Pop Culture Unplugged to talk about her exciting new role as Sabrina Grimm in Apple TV+’s animated fantasy adventure The Sisters Grimm. In this interview, Ariel shares what drew her to the series, how she connected with Sabrina, and what makes this magical, fairy-tale-meets-mystery world so special...
